selectHotelObj.name: Sofitel Singapore City Centre

Property Location

Rooms
Make yourself at home in one of the 223 air-conditioned rooms featuring minibars and LED televisions. Complimentary wired and wireless Internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming provides entertainment. Private bathrooms with separate bathtubs and showers feature designer toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include laptop-compatible safes and desks, and housekeeping is provided daily.

Amenities
Take advantage of recreation opportunities including an outdoor pool and a 24-hour fitness center. This hotel also features complimentary wireless Internet access, concierge services, and a picnic area.

Dining
Enjoy a meal at a restaurant or in a coffee shop/café. Or stay in and take advantage of the hotel's 24-hour room service. Quench your thirst with your favorite drink at a bar/lounge.

Business, Other Amenities
Featured amenities include complimentary wired Internet access, a business center, and express check-out. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite.

hotels.name: Equarius Sentosa
hotels.description:
Discover a precious pearl at the southernmost tip of continental Asia. Situated along the fringe of a tropical rainforest on Sentosa, the Equarius Hotel ensconces guests in a haven of lush greenery. An integral part of Resorts World Sentosa, the Equarius Hotel is the perfect getaway for nature lovers and families alike and is a stone's throw from nature hikes amidst verdant grounds and the island's numerous attractions, including a water theme park that is opening soon. Guests are accommodated in oversized deluxe rooms and suites, boasting balconies with gracious, panoramic views of either forest or sea, in deference to nature. A full complement of luxurious in-room amenities coupled with round-the-clock room service ensures a peerless stay experience. Guests are assured of a superior slumber on luxe mattresses paired with 400 thread count Egyptian cotton bed linen in all guestrooms, and spacious bathrooms with double vanity areas, tubs and separate showers. Guests staying in suite rooms can also take advantage of customized pillow menus and exclusive 24-hour personal butler service. An exquisite dining experience awaits guests at Forest, a unique dining concept helmed by renowned celebrity chef Sam Leong. Guests dine under a forest canopy inspired ceiling, whilst savoring Chef Leong's signature flavorful creations. Equarius Hotel is also complemented by a full level devoted to meeting and function rooms to suit every purpose. Guests at Equarius Hotel are simply spoilt for choice.
Resorts World Sentosa is a mere 10 minutes from Singapore Central Business District, and is easily accessible via reliable, convenient and extremely affordable modes of transportation i.e. buses, MRT rail system, cabs and cars. One can also take a leisurely stroll from VivoCity shopping mall to the resort.
Deluxe Room - Guests are accommodated in oversized deluxe rooms of at least 65sqm, boasting balconies with coffee tables that overlook panoramic views of either forest or sea, in deference to nature. A large L-shaped settee and multi-directional TV rack ensures optimal comfort for both living and entertaining, while superior slumber is guaranteed on luxe mattresses paired with 400 thread count Egyptian cotton bed linen. Spacious bathrooms boast double vanity areas, large bathtubs with separate rain-shower chambers and a clear screen affording a view of the bedroom, that turns opaque for privacy at the flick of a switch. Equarius Hotel's luxurious in-room amenities coupled with round-the-clock room service ensures every guest a peerless stay experience.Room amenities: Balcony panoramic or forest/sea view, iHome Docking Station, Minibar, Iron & Ironing Board, Kettle with Coffee & Tea Service, 42 Plasma TV with Cable Vision

hotels.name: Hotel Michael
hotels.description: Located on Sentosa Island, the hotel is a mere 10-minute drive from Singapore's Central Business District and is easily accessible via reliable, convenient and extremely affordable modes of transportation like buses, the MRT rail system, cabs and cars. Guests can take a leisurely stroll to VivoCity (about 10 minutes). Palawan Beach is about 10 minutes' walk away. Singapore Changi Airport is situated at a distance of approximately 35 km.Built in 2010, this 473-room designer hotel is one of the 6 hotels linked to the first Integrated Resort in Singapore. Its unique designer lifestyle features signature artworks and interior design by famed designer and architect Michael Graves including a collection of his favourite objects, from lamps to crockery and lounge chairs to carpet. Guests are welcomed to the air-conditioned property in a lobby with 24-hour reception and check-out service, currency exchange facilities and lift access. The establishment also comprises an auditorium, casino, games room, café, bar, pub, breakfast/dining room and conference facilities. Internet access and room service are additionally provided and for a fee guests may take advantage of the laundry service and car park.The main concept of the rooms is the unique lifestyle featuring signature artworks and interior design by Michael Graves, for instance, the circular shower, hand drawn murals by the designer and stunning mosaic-tile wall. Wireless Internet connection is available in the rooms with a fee. All rooms are en suite and equipped with a hairdryer, double bed, direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV and radio. Furthermore, a safe, minibar, tea and coffee making facilities and individually regulated air conditioning feature as standard.
